# Optional: environment variables for tools used by agent skills.
#
# QMD — vault search (CLI / MCP). See README.md.
#
# Google Workspace CLI (`gws`) — Docs, Drive, Calendar, Gmail (read-only workflows).
# Auth and tokens are normally stored under ~/.config/gws/ after `gws auth login`.
# Optional overrides (see https://github.com/googleworkspace/cli ):
#
# GOOGLE_WORKSPACE_CLI_CONFIG_DIR=/path/to/config
# GOOGLE_WORKSPACE_CLI_CREDENTIALS_FILE=/path/to/credentials.json
# GOOGLE_WORKSPACE_CLI_TOKEN=...   # pre-obtained access token (advanced)
